<refnamediv><refname>opencv_zoo_gui</refname><refpurpose>Browse and download official OpenCV Zoo models.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>opencv_zoo_gui()</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>opencv_zoo_gui</function> opens the IPCV browser interface for the official OpenCV Zoo. Models are grouped by task and can be downloaded with their companion assets. The interface can also generate and open a starter Scilab inference script.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[
opencv_zoo_gui();
]]></programlisting></refsection>
